Revision history for Packager (ordered by revision number).

0.1.4 Jan 14 2019
   - [FIX] Fix symlink creation
   - [FIX] Improve detection of fpm errors

0.1.3 Dec 01 2018
   - [FEATURE] Add support for symbolic links.

0.1.2 Nov 30 2018
   - [FEATURE] Add support for the following flags:
       * --before-install (aliased as --pre-install)
       * --after-install (aliased as --post-install)
       * --before-remove (aliased as --pre-uninstall)
       * --after-remove (aliased as --post-uninstall)
       * --before-upgrade
       * --after-upgrade

0.1.1 Nov 10 2018
   - [FEATURE] Add the ability to provide variables
   - [FEATURE] Add the ability to specify `--dryrun`

0.1.0 Nov 08 2018
   - Update license to MIT
   - Update dsl-maker dependency to 1.0.0 for its license to be MIT
   - Update yard dependency per GitHub security alert

0.0.1 Aug 03 2015
   - Initial release
